import { Form, Button, Modal, Row, Col } from 'react-bootstrap';
import React, { useContext } from 'react';
import { ModeContext } from './ModeContext';
function Mode(props) {
  const [show, setShow] = useContext(ModeContext);
  return (

    <Modal show={show} onHide={() => setShow(false)} style={{ position: 'fixed', zIndex: '999999999999' }}>
      <Modal.Header closeButton>
        <Modal.Title>Rukn Aljazeera Services Provider:</Modal.Title>
      </Modal.Header>
      <Modal.Body>
        <Form className="ContactForm" style={{ width: '100%' }}>
          <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="exampleForm.ControlInput1">
            <Form.Select aria-label="Default select example">
              <option>Choose The Services Please:</option>
              <option value="Leather upholstery">Leather upholstery</option>
              <option value="Outdoor, Pool, Garden">Outdoor, Pool, Garden</option>
              <option value="Sofas, Chairs, Stools">Sofas, Chairs, Stools</option>
              <option value="Partitions & Headboards">Partitions & Headboards</option>
            </Form.Select>
            </Form.Group>
            <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="exampleForm.ControlInput1">
              <Form.Control type="email" placeholder="email@example.com" />
            </Form.Group>
            <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="exampleForm.ControlInput1">
              <Form.Control type="tel" placeholder="tel: +971501234567" />
            </Form.Group>
            <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="exampleForm.ControlInput1">
              <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="full name" />
            </Form.Group>
            <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="exampleForm.ControlTextarea1">
              <Form.Control as="textarea" rows={3} placeholder='Leave a message' />
            </Form.Group>
            <Button>Booking Now</Button>
        </Form>
      </Modal.Body>
    </Modal>



  );
}

export default Mode;
